data.description: Great home with curb appeal and upgrades in Sunnyside. Fenced in back yard with a large deck and patio area perfect for entertaining. Remodeled kitchen and bathroom with new kitchen appliances and ceramic tile. Washer and dryer, roof, energy efficient windows, siding, hot water heater and HVAC System are all new! Home also has alarm and surveillance system installed and solar panels.
